Nika Futterman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nika_Futterman 0 Nika Futterman (born October 25, 1969) is an American voice actress and singer, best known for voicing Adam Lyon in My Gym Partner's A Monkey, Sticks the Badger in Sonic Boom, Luna Loud in The Loud House, and Asajj Ventress in Star Wars: The Clone Wars.
